name: Planes Of Being.
description:
You are constantly living simultaneously on three distinct planes of being: you are spiritual, you have an intellect, & you are living in a physical body.

The three distinct planes of existence as follows:
The spiritual plane of thought.
The intellectual plane of ideas.
The physical plane of results.

Some learning from Bob Proctor's 'You Were Born Rich'. Been taking in a lot of the informative content that he has left for us since his recent passing. This is something that stood out to me while listening to his audiobook & inspired this creation. Thank you Bob Proctor for the inspiration & teachings all of these years. Came across his work years ago after his appearance in "The Secret", which I love to believe helped me manifest a lot of positive results in the past. In recent years I forgot about all of this & could see how that alone has steered my mind elsewhere. I should definitely implement the law of attraction again..
